{"tid":150361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［現實］毒撚俾肥婆打完唔敢出聲","createTime":"2017-03-10T03:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T06:06:28.000Z","uid":13495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"904c61ef488780dbc8301dcbcd97f70138c74163","tid":150361,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:48:47.000Z","msg":"日本北海道札幌一名廿多歲女子，因為坐巴士優先座而遭一名十多歲少年勸止，2人先發生口角，後來女子向少年動粗，遭警方送交檢察當局處理。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上月18日，片段在網上廣傳，當時女子坐在少年左邊的優先座，少年就叫她不要霸佔優先座，2人繼而口角。女子怒氣沖沖走向少年身邊破口大罵，一手就將他的鴨舌帽撥開，然後扯住他的頭髮往後扯，再將自己的臉龐湊近少年，怒罵：「別開玩笑了，臭小子！」<br />\n<br />\n司機透過車上廣播系統勸止2人，但女子已情緒失控，一度走向車門又折返，再毆打少年頭部。少年遇襲後道：「司機，可以報警嗎？」女子大叫：「真吵，錯的是你吧？誰是大嬸啊。說說看吧！」<br />\n<br />\n少年事後報警求助，警方昨以暴行罪名將女子送交檢察當局跟進，女子亦都表示：「被人說是『大嬸』，怒氣沖心。」<br />\n<br />\n日本《北海道文化放送》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170309&amp;guid=56403347&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170309%26guid%3D56403347%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=4117b5b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170309%26guid%3D56403347%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=fad62184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170309&amp;guid=56403347&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909255ac51211569d1e1d9e37befd6fc30235917","tid":150361,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmB661h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmB661h.jpg&h=fce79ed8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d24a0bc9b382caaea5d4221b686760b14e722d67","tid":150361,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmB661h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmB661h.jpg&h=fce79ed8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1759637af4c42ce373708956f7f412df3f11c9bb","tid":150361,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"日本絲打打得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成架車都無乜人都唔撚比人坐貼紙位<br />\n食屎啦道德撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68068e91ac803fbf7bc0d218e39150f0a42a122d","tid":150361,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:24:12.000Z","msg":"肥婆真係毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5bdca96df3e7415d40e26f50cba4f039b3b3a5","tid":150361,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:12:06.000Z","msg":"死肥婆"},{"pid":"d5f9c47130a9db2cf168572209273b8d2f5a0704","tid":150361,"uid":40842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"肥婆同讓座撚，兩個一樣乞人憎<br />\n但呢次肥婆沉唔住氣出手打人，真係幫唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693e927b04f3bcc3f5bcb9105d03f45955c1032c","tid":150361,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82a55717ef483d7ffa3eff09344fee7d3b047ed9","tid":150361,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"<b